### [SETUP-20] Crear partido: Equipo Stats A (local) vs Equipo Stats B (visitante)
# Partido creado directamente con POST /matches — team_stats_a es homeTeam
# homeGoals=2, awayGoals=0 → Equipo Stats A gana → points=3 (+1 FairPlay = 4)
POST {{host}}/matches
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{org_token}}

{
  "homeTeamId": {{team_stats_a_id}},
  "awayTeamId": {{team_stats_b_id}},
  "matchDate": "2026-07-15T16:00:00",
  "field": "Cancha Stats"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("match_stats_id", response.body.data.id.toString());
  client.log("✔ match_stats_id = " + response.body.data.id);
%}

###

### [SETUP-21] Iniciar partido → "En Curso"
PATCH {{host}}/matches/{{match_stats_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{org_token}}

{
  "status": "En Curso"
}

###

